public static enum Types.CommandResult
extends java.lang.Enum<Types.CommandResult>

Defines the possible result values of commands sent to devices.

Enum Constant Summary
COMMAND_CANCELLED
          Indicates that the AirFlinger SDK is shutting down before the command was processed
COMMAND_FAILED
          Indicates that the command sent to the device has failed
DEVICE_OFFLINE
          Indicates that the device you were trying to access is offline
INIT_ERROR
          Indicates that the AirFlinger SDK failed to initialize.
INVALID_COMMAND
          Indicates that the device does not support the requested command
INVALID_DEVICE
          Indicates that no device is known with the id specified
INVALID_INTERNAL_BUFFER_ERROR
          Indicates that the AirFlinger SDK service operation could not complete.
INVALID_PARAM
          Indicates that an invalid parameter was sent
OUT_OF_BOUNDS_ERROR
          Indicates that the AirFlinger SDK service operation caused deviation from allowed bounds
SERVICE_DISCONNECTED
          Indicates that the AirFlinger SDK service has disconnected from the application
SUCCESS
          Success
UNKNOWN_ERROR
          Indicates that an unknown error occurred
